<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br" data-theme="light">
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
        <title>{% block title %}DevBlog | Dashboard{% endblock %}</title>

        <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/daisyui@4.7.2/dist/full.min.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" />
        <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>

        <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
        <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

        <style>
            body { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; }
        </style>
    </head>
    <body class="bg-slate-50 min-h-screen">
        <div class="navbar bg-white border-b border-slate-200 px-4 md:px-20 mb-10">
            <div class="flex-1">
                <a href="/" class="text-xl font-bold text-indigo-600 tracking-tight">🚀 DevBlog</a>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-none gap-2">
                <ul class="menu menu-horizontal px-1 font-medium">
                    <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
                </ul>
                <div class="flex gap-2 ml-4">
                    <a href="/login" class="btn btn-ghost btn-sm">Entrar</a>
                    <a href="/register" class="btn btn-primary btn-sm px-6">Criar Conta</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
            {% block body %}
                <div class="card bg-white shadow-sm border border-slate-200">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h2 class="card-title text-2xl text-slate-800">Seu primeiro post aparecerá aqui!</h2>
                        <p class="text-slate-600">O backend já está configurado, agora é só criar a entidade para salvar no banco.</p>
                        <div class="card-actions justify-end mt-4">
                            <button class="btn btn-outline btn-sm">Ler mais</button>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            {% endblock %}
        </main>

        <footer class="footer footer-center p-10 text-slate-500 mt-20">
            <aside>
                <p class="font-bold">DevBlog Engineering</p> 
                <p>Copyright © 2026 - All right reserved</p>
            </aside>
        </footer>
    </body>
</html>